{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not army, but ammunition bunkers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had in the forest built bunkers where they had a lot of ammunition from the eastern front.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But only the roofs were sticking out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything was in the ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to clean the ammunition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes when there used to come some trains, we had to unload trains with calcium or-- I don't know what you actually call it in-- in English-- because they needed it for the-- what they couldn't cremate.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the bodies had to be buried, so they had to put some disinfectant on top.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know it in Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called 'vapno.' When it is raw, you put water to it and it boils.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It burns.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quick lime.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or we used to whitewash with it, you know, when they didn't have people in-- in-- a lot of houses used to be whitewashed with that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then in the winter-- that was in the summer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not even allowed to put rags on our hands when we were unloading it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it burned our skin sometime to the bone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the winter, I don't know what they needed for the iron baths.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to unload iron baths in the winter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know how iron is frozen, the skin used to stick to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's how it used to be with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Used to take us away from anywhere we were working when a train arrived with something we had to do, to help out with unloading.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't enough the men who were doing it, so we all had to help.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then from-- from--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, we were not allowed to be sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sick people were taken to the third camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
